Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:05.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爸妈终于给我买手机了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保存好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:52.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你买手机了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:03.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是最新款吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也正准备要买这款
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以摸摸看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 还挺轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为了今天绞尽脑汁才想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,用手机捉弄高木同学的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我就要用它战胜高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:42.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原本以为高木同学会问我要邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样下去就没法实施计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我主动去问高木同学不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我没有注意到这么简单的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把你的邮箱地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 我为什么要这么紧张 冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是找高木同学要她的邮箱地址而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:55.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我正在问女生要邮箱地址吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉这样…有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像是那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有什么事情想要问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还以为你想问我要邮箱地址呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不如说这正是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个问题只要回答Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能拿到她的邮箱地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你大意了啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你刚才为什么要糊弄过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是有什么事 联系起来就方便多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,例如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是有什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还问到了谁的邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:07.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村和高尾 还有中井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还没问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学是我问的第一个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以快点 快点把邮箱地址告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想和我交换邮箱地址吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:31.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有 我只是想用邮件来捉弄高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是像你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我真的一点奇怪的事情都没有想过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道会是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然你想捉弄我的计划泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我们还是来交换邮箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作为捉弄我的赔礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你下周要帮我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没有捉弄你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还没捉弄到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 如果没暴露的话就会捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这之前 我们到家再聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我在家里也会被她捉弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想要手机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是昨天和妈妈说的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她说我要买手机还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这么突然她肯定会这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你无论干什么都很突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不突然好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很久以前就想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很久以前是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大概一周前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看你这样子 应该是三天前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无论怎么样 都太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是什么呀 犯规了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超级大狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 现在有手机的同学也越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也有点想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对吧 你也想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家一起去拜托妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗也很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起来发邮件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我已经有一部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会有手机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为社团有时会弄得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以爸妈让我带着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说这种事情你倒是告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是说早苗也有的话说不定就会买给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也这样跟家里说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样一来就能得到手机了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起来发好多邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想在睡觉前玩接龙或者猜谜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:29.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是因为你这么说 你爸妈才不给你买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们来讲恐怖故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是最胆小的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们来试一试嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有天晚上 一个陌生的电话号码打了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接通电话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,听到的是一阵呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:56.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,慌慌张张地把电话挂断之后 对方却再也没有打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:56.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是因为太过在意 试着回拨了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然而 什么声音也没有听见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知为何 电话费竟高达十万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}「架空請求」，日本的电信诈骗的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太可怕了 电信诈骗太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明是由加莉更可怕好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恐怖故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你遵守之前的约定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好像很困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:07.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你熬夜看了录下来的百分百单相思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和班上的男生聊短信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聊了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 高木同学难得对这个话题感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次有手机的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和别人聊短信真的很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我当时也是聊到不能自拔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 家人就叫我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:45.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和高木同学聊短信的人 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:48.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和班上的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷静 之前也有过这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最后一次和我两个人一起骑车的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和你爸聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不会和爸爸聊短信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片告诉我男孩子之间会聊些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有个一石二鸟的好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你也就只有现在能悠哉悠哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:44.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,昨天男生们互发有趣的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎样的视频啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是木村发来的网址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把这个害我昨晚睡不好的视频…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你给我发了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有可爱动物的视频网站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难不成是色情网站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕得说不出话来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你总是在看这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我给你发的不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是问一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看西片给我发的视频吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又是这样 高木同学这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可爱啊 这个是山羊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 她放松警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快到时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被吓得魂飞魄散吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不对 你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为是在早上看的 所以也没那么害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来在发这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,男生真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学会和谁聊天 聊些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我聊的只是普通的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样根本不算回答嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对方名字的首字母是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是石井同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」之后是「to」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 是伊藤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是班上的伊藤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 最后一个字是「ko」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…「ko」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}日语中的「itoko」是指表或堂兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十七
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…九
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还以为今天肯定能捉弄到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,结果反过来被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 今天还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上不奏效 晚上发给她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家的时候木村发给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,更恐怖的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然因为太可怕了 我还没看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就把这个发给高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:30.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会又是什么要让我做俯卧撑的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 是西片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,发恐怖视频给我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以为这样就能揭露我的计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,胜负还…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「你好好期待着挂断电话之后会发生什么吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你差不多要睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次在晚上和西片说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有点小心动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那明天见 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还没挂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学来挂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我打给你的 西片来挂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们数一二 一起挂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今晚也睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猫在打架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你等一会 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保持这样 保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按快门的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 只拍到了墙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 突然拍什么照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们男生现在在比谁能拍出更有趣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在第一名是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村的这张遥遥领先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这张的冲击感很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.08,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs100\pos(500,212)}超市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.08,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fn@楷体\an7\frz270\pos(592,722)}大狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有趣的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 让我拍拍你的鬼脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那张绝对能比过超级大狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片什么都愿意做的话就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么都？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是什么都答应我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明这里就有一位能冲击第一名的种子选手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:07.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明给你拍照机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她可是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,尝到甜头之后肯定还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在就装作一副失落的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看吧 她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍照的机会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是玩具蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你刚才拍我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 快删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要 我好不容易才拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要是什么都愿意做的话 我就把它删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个计划也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是拍到好照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也要看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还是连拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这表情变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:30.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要把你这副咧着嘴笑得像个傻子一样的表情拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定会羞得抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍好看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样一来就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪里扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:49.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把这张删掉 你也把那些删了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不删
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:54.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以你不删我的照片也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她心情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明我一张有趣的照片也没拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的照片 不可以给别人看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 我怎么会给别人看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道别人会说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太危险了 还是删了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她说她会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定哪天和她谈判的时候能用到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先留着吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:17.99,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:22.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:32.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:41.56,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.78,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:58.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.04,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.96,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:14.05,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:27.77,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.77,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:41.99,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:17.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:22.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:32.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:41.56,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.78,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:58.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.04,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:14.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:27.77,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.77,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:41.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:16.10,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}広い宇宙の数ある一つ　青い地球の広い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:25.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}小さな恋の思いは届く　小さな島のあなたのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:31.12,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出会い　時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:35.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}思いをこめた　手紙もふえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:40.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いつしか二人互いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:45.42,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時に激しく　時に切なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:50.09,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響くは遠く　遥か彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:54.85,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}優しい歌は　世界を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　あなたにとって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大事な人ほど　すぐそばにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:13.78,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただあなたにだけ　届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響け恋の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:26.13,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:35.47,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　響け恋の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:16.10,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把这辽阔宇宙中绝无仅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:25.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}传达给蔚蓝地球上广阔世界中小小岛屿上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:31.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}与你邂逅 光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:35.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}饱含思念的信件堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:40.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不觉我们心生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:45.42,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}时而充满激情 时而伤感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:50.09,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}回响渐渐远去 到那遥远彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:54.85,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那温柔的歌声 改变了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 对你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:13.78,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只愿你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:26.13,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你听 你听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:31.47,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:35.47,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
